\p
\v 30 \add They committed to\add* not giving their daughters to the \add other\add* \add вүҲpeople groups\add* inВҰ226581 the land, and to not taking their daughters for their sons.\x + \xo 10:30: \xt Exo 34:16; Deu 7:3.\x*
