\p
\v 37 We will bringВҰ226746 our offerings and the first of our flour, and the fruit of every tree, wine, and oil, for the priestsВҰ226749, to the \add вүҲtemple storerooms\add*, and a tenth of our \add вүҲproduce\add* for the Levites.
\p The Levites will be the ones receiving a tenth \add of our cash income\add* inВҰ226740 all the towns \add вүҲwhere we work\add*.\x + \xo 10:37: \xt Num 18:21.\x*
\v 38 A priestВҰ226767 who's a descendant of Aharon must be withВҰ226780 \add *them\add* when theyВҰ226777 collectВҰ226779 the tenths, then the LevitesВҰ226776 must take a tenth of that to the \add вүҲtemple\add* to be placed inВҰ226780 their treasury rooms.\x + \xo 10:38: \xt Num 18:26.\x*
\v 39 The \add вүҲIsraelis\add* and the \add вүҲLevitesВҰ226792\add* must bringВҰ226796 the offerings of grain, wine, and oil to the storeroomsВҰ226805. There must \add also\add* be \add вүҲutensils\add* for the sanctuary and the priestsВҰ226786, for the ones who are ministering and the gatekeepers, and for the \add вүҲsingers\add*.
\p We mustn't neglect our god's house.
